---
title: Sugar-Rubbed Pork Chops with Caramelized Root Vegetables
description: A sweet and spicy sugar rub makes these pork chops unreasonably delectable. Served with caramelized parsnips, carrots, and pearl onions. This dish strikes the perfect balance of savory and sweet. A simple dizzle of pan sauce takes this recipe form delicious to restaurant-worthy.
